rows.label: bf11300100_0030
rows.name:
A face that ugly, I couldn't forget.
Trust me, I tried!

rows.label: bf11300100_0050
rows.name:
What do you want?
Not that I can't imagine.

rows.label: bf11300100_0060
rows.name: I'm here to take back what's mine, kid.

rows.label: bf11300100_0075
rows.name:
I'll take a bit o' time to
express my gratitude to ya.

rows.label: bf11300100_0080
rows.name: It ain't gonna be pretty or quick.

rows.label: bf11300100_0090
rows.name:
Then I'll make that Blade watch
as I cut you into little, sticky chunks.

rows.label: bf11300100_0100
rows.name:
Just to make sure the last thing
he feels is complete despair.

rows.label: bf11300100_0110
rows.name:
I'll hold them up.
You get to the others, quickly.

rows.label: bf11300100_0130
rows.name:
Kasumi, he knew about you.
He brought no Blades, just mercs.

rows.label: bf11300100_0155
rows.name:
I'm gonna treat you real good
'fore I get to the cuttin'.
